{
  "3036800": {
    "name": "普力多 普力兹纳",
    "steam_appid": 3036800,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/0b09ec339c036c285258202c4234987d.poster.avif?t=1768240988\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/0b09ec339c036c285258202c4234987d.webm?t=1768240988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/0b09ec339c036c285258202c4234987d.mp4?t=1768240988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到监狱岛，这里戒备森严，是世界上最可爱又最不靠谱的监狱。调皮的动物囚犯正在谋划各种荒唐的越狱计划，希望逃出海岛，加班过度的机器人守卫也只能勉强应对。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款混乱的4v2非对称派对游戏：四名动物玩家联手破坏监狱，完成乱七八糟的目标，悄悄通过一道又一道逃生门。两名机器人玩家要协作抓住他们，送进“小睡室”短暂关押，阻止他们逃脱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过，监狱岛上越狱从来都不会顺利。各位动物需要以意想不到的方式运用屎尿超能力，让每一次越狱混乱又搞笑。因此，每一次行动都会变成滑稽的喜剧，动物调皮淘气，机器人筋疲力尽，勉强维持监狱现状，防止解体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/bf3be75d3f36b9db05467a8fea99fedc.avif?t=1768240988\" width=920 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">成为监狱岛上误入歧途（但很可爱）的高风险居民，你们个个背景离奇，而且肠胃和膀胱一刻也停不下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/cb22d1b63f0b94d3f8a773282f546860.poster.avif?t=1768240988\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/cb22d1b63f0b94d3f8a773282f546860.webm?t=1768240988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/cb22d1b63f0b94d3f8a773282f546860.mp4?t=1768240988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><strong>通力合作，逃出海岛</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">组队或单独排队完成无厘头的任务，协调离谱的越狱计划，施展巧妙的策略，运用混乱的身体机能。时刻保持警惕，因为一次失误就有可能把你直接送进小睡室！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/8c6273f79daa8fcbb335883c3b311825.poster.avif?t=1768240988\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/8c6273f79daa8fcbb335883c3b311825.webm?t=1768240988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/8c6273f79daa8fcbb335883c3b311825.mp4?t=1768240988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><strong>选择你的动物囚犯</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">动物的能力和性格各不相同。不论你要当狮子剑客，砍翻机器人，还是当大象艺术品诈骗犯，把机器人耍得团团转，或者用你的能力制造纯粹的混乱，每一次游戏都会让你有不一样的混乱和逃脱体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/131adcedc73de2ee3efb1ca3e13476e4.avif?t=1768240988\" width=920 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">叫上一个伙伴，依靠可以自定义的机器人零件、强大的工具以及可以持续抵御……“奇怪液体”的电路，追捕企图越狱的囚犯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/0291e8b3b9c554d5d830646885a7d4f0.poster.avif?t=1768240988\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/0291e8b3b9c554d5d830646885a7d4f0.webm?t=1768240988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/0291e8b3b9c554d5d830646885a7d4f0.mp4?t=1768240988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><strong>机器人部件自由搭配</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">使用可以互换的零件组建你的机器人，将上半身与下半身组合，以你自己的方式完成抓捕。攻击方式任你选择，既有电击枪可以击晕距离近的动物，也可以用套索拿下远处的目标。行动方式也可以变换，既有轮子方便高速追逐，也有坦克履带可以直接碾压障碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/2abab81e67607efa4181a322e7716e08.poster.avif?t=1768240988\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/2abab81e67607efa4181a322e7716e08.webm?t=1768240988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/2abab81e67607efa4181a322e7716e08.mp4?t=1768240988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><strong>选择你的工具和强化装置</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">根据你的追捕策略，给你的机器人配备主动工具和被动强化装置。神奇手臂可以布设陷阱，虫洞能够穿墙，然后配合护盾防御，或者配合伪装，能在原地不动时隐身。每次对战都能收集噗噗蛋解锁强大的升级项目，让你的机器人战斗力更强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3036800/extras/8728fd7f55cd67036a2ddbd435a1ab0f.avif?t=1768240988\" width=920 height=139 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●      看起来可爱，一片混乱！享受动物队和机器人队之间<strong>快节奏的非对称4v2对战</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●      对战时间短，<strong>10分钟一场</strong>，非常适合派对或者随时随地都能玩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●      战斗系统<strong>围绕排泄机制设计</strong>，滑稽是滑稽，但也很讲究策略</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●      <strong>Kanahei</strong>的萌系画风搭配<strong>TeddyLoid</strong>的活力音乐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●      所有平台均<strong>全面支持跨平台对战</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●      <strong>单人剧情模式</strong>揭晓监狱岛不为人知的古怪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●      完成挑战可以获得<strong>普力多硬币</strong>，还能解锁有趣的自定义物品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●      动物和机器人都有各自<strong>专属的自定义皮肤和装饰</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●      <strong>私密对战</strong>模式可以与好友自行定义游戏规则</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 日语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 韩语",
